{"tid":15668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"協助他人爆竊炫富鄰居偷23萬財物 綜援婦囚20個月","createTime":"2016-12-01T05:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T10:49:21.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d1cfca04671f6d2b4e11316723732bb747c089","tid":15668,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:50:41.000Z","msg":"協助他人爆竊炫富鄰居偷23萬財物 綜援婦囚20個月<br />\n<br />\n居於公屋的離婚綜援婦聲稱因急於替父母籌醫藥費，協助三名賊人爆竊不時談論自己買名牌的鄰居，賊人偷去鄰居3隻勞力士手錶、3個LV和1個Gucci手袋、金頸鏈及現金等共值23萬元的財物，事後婦人獲分一隻金色勞力士手錶。她今在區院承爆竊罪，被判囚20個月。<br />\n<br />\n於2003年來港的被告王淑琴（46歲），今求情指要獨力撫養18和12歲女兒，她因急於為居內地的七旬父母籌醫藥費而犯案，現已非常後悔。法官指本案犯案者多於一人、事主被偷去大量財物而且大部分未尋回，這些均是加刑因素，惟考慮被告認罪並要照顧兩女，判被告入獄20個月。<br />\n<br />\n案發於今年4月19日，住於將軍澳健明邨的被告警誡下指，案發日的前一天，有一名男子問她哪裏有富貴人家，被告稱常聽到鄰居談論買名牌，被告於翌日協助對方與兩名不明人士由後門進入大廈，三人進入涉事單位犯案。事主被偷去1部iPad、6件首飾、1隻黑色和2隻金銀色勞力士、2條金頸鏈、3個LV和1個Gucci手袋、1條手鏈、現金7,000元及護照和出世紙。被告獲分一隻金色勞力士手錶，變賣後得6,000元。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45cb30a6dfe3a09fd4eb8c95142f12dae81b8ed0","tid":15668,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:52:09.000Z","msg":"正評👍🏻"},{"pid":"1492f65af78714f55da206e8f64384da0aa758b0","tid":15668,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"成抽野加埋得廿三萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個三隻係咩勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf06417385ff9ec88ff0b25ddead3b130783d6e0","tid":15668,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成抽野加埋得廿三萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個三隻係咩勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻金撈變賣得六千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8190c57801e8474c8ebf504cdc1a961a35674e","tid":15668,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:05:11.000Z","msg":"典型偽有錢人 淨係識買LV gucci同rolex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f008baf1e3e9e1af2276c2be0dc5fa69c8d05f6b","tid":15668,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:20:36.000Z","msg":"護照同出世紙都偷 , 做賊都做得低賤過人"},{"pid":"2b93209745586fca93d0809355ad5d6d12c46c45","tid":15668,"uid":19305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"咩撈得6000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e39016af891bfe52802f4b58b822e4be42ff83","tid":15668,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩撈得6000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n膠撈"},{"pid":"c34b451d64c3064d4e5f2ae7aff964a1e09580b9","tid":15668,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩撈得6000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n二叔公睇死係賊贓，賤價收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc570a610023bfafa9ef61700a250392450fc856","tid":15668,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}